high_descs: Walk across the room to reach the corner shelf where the bread and apple are.
Pick up the green apple from the shelf.
Right right to walk to the sink.
Rinse the apple in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Turn left to walk to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Rinse an apple to put it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the white stove and walk to the counter.
Pick up the green apple from the middle of the shelf above the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the apple inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the microwave on the shelf above the counter to the right.
Put the rinsed apple inside the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed apple in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room and turn to the left to face the counter with a shelf above it.
Pick the apple up from the shelf.
Turn around and then to the left to face the sink.
Put the apple in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the apple up again.
Turn around and turn to face the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean apple in the microwave.
